incidents.name: Cloudflare Dashboard and Cloudflare API service issues for users in China

incident_updates.body: The issue has been identified and a fix is being implemented.

affected_components.name: Cloudflare Sites and Services - Cloudflare Dashboard
Cloudflare Sites and Services - Cloudflare API

incident_updates.body: We are continuing to investigate this issue.

affected_components.name: Cloudflare Sites and Services - Cloudflare Dashboard
Cloudflare Sites and Services - Cloudflare API

incident_updates.body:
Cloudflare is investigating issues with Cloudflare Dashboard and related APIs for users in China.

These issues do not affect the serving of cached files via the Cloudflare CDN or other security features at the Cloudflare Edge.

Customers using the Dashboard / Cloudflare APIs from China are impacted as requests might fail and/or errors may be displayed.
